Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.29,0:01:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提炼纯度的问题还是没有解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.43,0:02:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上结晶方向还是不够一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.36,0:02:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这也已经超过标准了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.67,0:02:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以这里的设备来说 这已经是极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.74,0:02:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们“马克思”的商品比正规品还要高级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.47,0:02:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不容许出现任何暇疵品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重做！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.21,0:02:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 有人来搜查？ 难道是GOTT？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是GOTT的强制搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.45,0:02:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们涉嫌重力控制媒介“Hi-G”的非法制造及贩卖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.33,0:02:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.93,0:02:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是GOTT的ES成员Alv（注：Elf）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.57,0:02:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dvergr（注：Dwarf）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开枪！开枪！你们在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二话 重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那件案子的没收品啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就“Hi-G”来说这个容器还真大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.64,0:03:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，要小心点喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.37,0:04:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忌妒是很难看的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然同样是ES成员 但她们是S级的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.17,0:04:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等级比我们还高很多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.11,0:04:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是忌妒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是看不惯她们的态度而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有可以相提并论的实力的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不会有厌恶的感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是空的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，报告上说的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.96,0:04:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,封装方面也没有任何异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声东击西…？ 陷阱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们居然被设计了…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.31,0:05:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mercredi，这件事交给Tweedledee跟Tweedledum
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.68,0:05:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的耻辱希望能由我们自己来弥补
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.98,0:05:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么就为你们准备支援人员吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.89,0:05:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带Eclair、Lumiere去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，局长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，也请Armbrust监察官过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.34,0:05:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双子星Latium及Latinus
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.68,0:05:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人工收容所Globe Cage\N就围绕着它的极限轨道运行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经确认过身份的马克思成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都被收容于此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.62,0:05:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不用为了取证而特地跑到那种地方吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有拜讬你一起过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是局长的命令我才不来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.93,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有说些什么吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有说啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.08,0:06:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这么靠近的极限轨道上居然还没有被溶化掉耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.12,0:06:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都有赖于超过正常30倍的重力缓冲控制系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.49,0:06:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果控制系统完蛋的话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收容所当场变成火葬场？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可真是服务周到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我留在这里等你们好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.16,0:06:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船的自动诱导系统虽然正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.66,0:07:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但通常应该会有狱警来负责控制吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们吃完午饭之后又睡个午觉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.97,0:07:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在期待什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.34,0:07:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不过来的话就把你们丢在这里了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我们行动是你的工作耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随你高兴好了，怠忽职守监察官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.91,0:07:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是个打扫机械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Hi-G”的箱子空了之后\N紧接着是空荡荡的收容所？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是低劣的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，尸体有那么稀奇吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.53,0:08:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.31,0:08:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体好重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.69,0:08:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是重力炸弹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alv，用反射装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.09,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，就只会耍些骗小孩的把戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.19,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之，应该逮捕的活证人都已经被灭口了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情结束了，打道回府吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.57,0:09:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，举手之劳帮个忙也好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.07,0:09:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔？ 没听说过有哪个ES成员会为了这种事情求救的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪里…那个重力炸弹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,物理防御盾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.52,0:10:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多保重了，小姐们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.93,0:10:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事…我刚刚…找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.57,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但搞不好太迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.31,0:10:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，终于停下来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.05,0:10:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要崩溃了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.32,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在内部使用了两次重力炸弹那是当然的罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.92,0:10:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史瓦尔多…我们的船不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.59,0:10:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去！那个家伙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.37,0:11:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜啊，已经来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.52,0:11:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，总算来得…啊～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.66,0:12:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来，这个地方已经变得相当脆弱了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.29,0:12:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子…要优雅一点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船想去救她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.41,0:12:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La Muse！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它来救我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.98,0:13:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armbrust他…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.55,0:13:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夺走“Hi-G”、还有我们的船的全都是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…那个浑蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还没打开来看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.83,0:13:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用看也知道内容…对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要念了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.62,0:14:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然选这种地方当交易场所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.49,0:14:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你对古典的东西还蛮有兴趣的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.23,0:14:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是行星联合的官员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是守时啊，杂耍师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.14,0:14:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的匿称是“Magician”（注：魔术师）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.61,0:14:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不好吧，是立体影像吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.34,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界上只有“小心”才是长寿的秘诀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“马克思”那伙人就连这点也不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然那个重力炸弹是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是商品测试啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.42,0:14:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力炸弹加上重力地雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我们“休巴”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.33,0:14:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有原料的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论多少都可以生产出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是“Hi-G”吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.78,0:15:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，似乎是真品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.61,0:15:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在非活性状态下重力偏差值0.2吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.32,0:15:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是上等货，而且量也很够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.45,0:15:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来似乎很合您的胃口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.46,0:15:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有考虑过放弃制造武器改制造人工重力系统呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这玩笑真是有意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有比武器更值钱的商品的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就教教我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高额的利润伴随而来的就是高度的风险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在学校难道没有学过吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.15,0:15:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道是这么一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.68,0:15:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谎言跟背叛或许是你最厉害的功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.85,0:15:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我已经受够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手脚还真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.92,0:15:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经请“她”好好保护你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.90,0:16:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀…还真像是VIP级的待遇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意设下陷阱的吗？ 杂耍的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.75,0:16:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donnersclac 那个诈欺犯就交给你罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是“Magician”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.80,0:16:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧！只能撑住一发而已吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.61,0:16:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样很危险呢，Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，被防御盾干扰到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.48,0:17:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.67,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以GOTT直属ES成员的权力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.79,0:18:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指控你们为星际罪犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.03,0:18:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局长，我要申请逮捕执行权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.83,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,申请核准，Eclair、Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.41,0:18:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕？太愚蠢了 难道你们想逮捕立体影像吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.88,0:18:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，你还没发现吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，辛苦你们诱敌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局长，紧接着“马克思”之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.03,0:18:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“休巴”的据点也瓦解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.63,0:18:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，Alv、Dvergr
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.87,0:18:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为我会这么简单的束手就擒吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力炸弹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次你们躲不掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.19,0:19:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere只要在可以接近目标的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.16,0:19:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以强制夺取操纵系统的控制权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.33,0:19:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何况是这么近的距离…对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.90,0:19:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很坚固的箱子吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我最自傲的好东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，却让你把它弄坏了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.75,0:19:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过"这是我最自傲的好东西"吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两个老是抓不到的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.23,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉由老兄你的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总算把两方面的人马都扫除殆尽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.17,0:20:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“马克思”或是“休巴”早晚都会自已垮掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.51,0:20:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要让那群家伙继续胡作非为下去那我可受不了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这区域内28个殖民地的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.27,0:20:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这么说的话会不会成为笑柄呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.41,0:20:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个爱装模作样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低着床率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.89,0:20:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生后的畸形比率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.59,0:20:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及免疫系统功能降低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的低重力条件下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对宝宝而言绝对不是个好环境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.90,0:20:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我们是听说了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.07,0:21:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…这是真的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.27,0:21:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个殖民地也终于有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.97,0:21:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家期盼了好久的“人工重力调整室”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的…\N玛莉亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.94,0:21:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说我们可以像在地球一样生育孩子了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快出发到下个殖民地吧
